SELECT TID,Tamount,Tto,Uname,Tdatetime,'Outcome' as `Ttype` FROM `transaction` JOIN `user` ON `transaction`.`Tto`=`user`.`UID`  WHERE Tfrom='2'
SELECT TID,Tamount,Tfrom,Uname,Tdatetime,'Income' as `Ttype` FROM `transaction` JOIN `user` ON `transaction`.`Tfrom`=`user`.`UID`  WHERE Tto='2'
